{
  "texts": [
    "The accuracy values that we get from running InceptionV3 with different batch sizes, learning rates, and dropout period configurations are what are used to gather the data.",
    "The sample size of each equals 6.",
    "To assess the suitability of statistical analysis, normality and homogeneity of variance are verified.",
    "These tests are common prerequisites for many statistical tests.",
    "First, for the normality test, the Shapiro-Wilk test is applied to assess the normality assumption for each variable."
  ]
}